        {
            "id": 5908812,
            "title": "《再戰明天》日本及美國公布PMI,比亞迪舜宇康師傅公布業績",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社21日專訊》日本及美國公布PMI,及比亞迪舜宇康師傅公布業績,料為下周一(24日)市場焦點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*日本央行公布貨幣政策會議記錄,德國公布進口物價*</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　各國重要經濟活動方面,本港時間下周一7:50am,日本央行公布1月23至24日貨幣政策會議記錄。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　數據方面,下周一(24日)德國公布2月進口物價。8:30am(本港時間.下同),日本公布3月製造業採購經理人指數;3月綜合採購經理人指數;3月服務業採購經理人指數。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">9:45pm,美國公布3月製造業採購經理人指數,料由52.7降至51.8;3月綜合採購經理人指數;3月服務業採購經理人指數料由51升至51.2。</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　在本港,下周一(24日)公布業績的公司有:粵海投資(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00270:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00270\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00270-HK</a>)、比亞迪電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00285-HK</a>)、康師傅控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00322:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00322\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00322-HK</a>)、中國太平(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00966:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00966\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00966-HK</a>)、比亞迪股份(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01211-HK</a>)、舜宇光學科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02382-HK</a>)等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　下周二(25日)公布業績的公司有:昆侖能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00135:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00135\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00135-HK</a>)、光大環境(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00257:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00257\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00257-HK</a>)、萬洲國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00288:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00288\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00288-HK</a>)、中國中藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00570:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00570\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00570-HK</a>)、快手-W(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01024:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01024\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" 